snippet: Andy Murray kept on track to claim a record fifth title at Queen's Club by beating fellow Briton Aljaz Bedene 6-3, 6-4 to reach the quarterfinals on Thursday....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray kept on track to claim a record fifth title at Queen's Club by beating fellow Briton Aljaz Bedene 6-3, 6-4 to reach the quarterfinals on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Murray Eases Into Queen's Club Quarterfinals
headline.main: Murray Eases Into Queen's Club Quarterfinals
